Three day plan

14-feb-2025 saturday ( Banglore to madikeri around 300KM travel time: 7 hrs )

Stay should be in madikeri

~ Abbey fall vist just site visit.
~ Around 2'0 clock room check-in
~ Visit Glass bridge coffee plantation  (Open till 6PM).
~ Dinner at local shop
* check any falls to take bath via travel route.

Night stay - three hills coorg
coorg annu stays and cottage

15-feb-25 sunday
 
~ Before 6AM mandalpatti jeep safari should reach. 
~ Dubare River rafting
~ mallalli waterfalls
~ Evening vist raja seet sunset

Night stay

16-feb-25 monday (Return to banglore)

~ Tibetian temple
~ Mysore palace
~ Towards banglore



